org.drip.param.market

Class MarketParamsContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.drip.param.definition.MarketParams
      • org.drip.param.market.MarketParamsContainer

  • public class MarketParamsContainer
extends MarketParams
    This class serves as the place holder for the comprehensive suite of the market set of curves for the given date. Contains treasury quote map, fixings map, IR scenario curve map, credit curve scenario set map, and component quote map.
